oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:title: Songwriter Session- Rodney Crowell - 2013-09-21
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:description: Performance by Rodney Crowell from the Ford Theater at the Country Music Hall of Fame and Museum on September 21, 2013. Presented in partnership with the Americana Music Association. Guest appearance by Shannon McNally.
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dc:creator: Rodney Crowell; Shannon McNally;
oai_qdc:qualifieddc.dcterms:tableOfContents: Includes questions from the audience. Performances include; It's Hard To Kiss The Lips At Night That Chew Your Ass Out All Day Long -- Love Is All I Need -- Song For The Life -- Rock My Soul (Shannon McNally) -- East Houston Blues;
